        "action": "Tax companies that offshore jobs",
        "additional_details": "Any company that offshores jobs should be taxed so that the salary paid equals the average UK salary for the same role.\r\n\r\nThis would provide a level playing field and help young people gain employment in fields such as IT.\r\n\r\nThis is particularly the case for government owned companies like the big banks who have recently offshored many roles to India. ",
